keyFacts: Ghislaine N. Maxwell applied for a firearms license on February 21, 2006.
The firearms license was first issued on November 2, 2006, and later canceled on November 16, 2009.
Richard Barnett is noted as an associate in relation to the firearms license application.
The license was associated with a Glock 19 pistol, which was sold to a gun dealer.
The license was canceled due to Maxwell moving out of the city or state.
